Title : Mart McChesney
Text : '''Mart Dayne McChesney''' (January 27, 1954 â€“ January 14, 1999) was an American television and film actor known for his appearances in ''[[Star Trek: The Next Generation]]'' as the tar creature, Armus, in "[[Skin of Evil]]" (1988), and as Sheliak in "[[The Ensigns of Command]]" (1989). For his appearances he wore heavy [[prosthetics]] and costumes.<ref>http://en.memory-alpha.org/wiki/Mart_McChesney.</ref> Footage of his appearance as Armus was re-used in the Star Trek: The Next Generation second-season episode "[[Shades of Gray (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Shades of Gray]]" (1989). McChesney also appeared as Pete 'Maniac' Krizaniac in the [[horror film]], ''[[Girls Nite Out]]'' (1982).

McChesney was born in [[Abilene, Texas]], and died in [[Hollywood, Los Angeles]].<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0565573/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm.</ref>

